  "detailed_description": "There's been a lot of UFO sightings above the neighbourhood lately. <br>People are reporting their trees have gone missing! <br>Time to assemble the Treefenders: an alliance of neighbourhood kids, determined to keep the suburban trees save!<br><br><strong>Relive your childhood in Treefender, a VR-exclusive 4 player online co-op base-building game <br>where you build your own treefort and defend it against a spacesquid invasion!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build</h2>The treefort of your nostalgic dreams. With intuitive buildtools and many buildpieces to pick from.<br>Find valuable mushrooms spread out across the neigbourhood for Koinz to unlock new, wacky stuff to build.<br>Add decorations to your fort to earn more Koinz.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/c68512d84c04b2c4e2f5f41e14998284.poster.avif?t=1720096938\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/c68512d84c04b2c4e2f5f41e14998284.webm?t=1720096938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/c68512d84c04b2c4e2f5f41e14998284.mp4?t=1720096938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend</h2>Yourself, and your buddies (4 player online co-op) against grumpy space squids, set out to harvest every tree in the universe!<br>Use everything in your Treefender arsenal: slingshots, exploding gardengnomes, makeshift drones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/a0b5f84c32b43195c2c491e3c42f9741.poster.avif?t=1720096938\" width=300 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/a0b5f84c32b43195c2c491e3c42f9741.webm?t=1720096938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Expand</h2>Your treefort with new abilities, wonky buildobjects and wacky weapons you research.<br>The squiddies won't know what hit 'em!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/11aa053d4489b753d4514581ccac4515.poster.avif?t=1720096938\" width=300 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/11aa053d4489b753d4514581ccac4515.webm?t=1720096938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "There's been a lot of UFO sightings above the neighbourhood lately. <br>People are reporting their trees have gone missing! <br>Time to assemble the Treefenders: an alliance of neighbourhood kids, determined to keep the suburban trees save!<br><br><strong>Relive your childhood in Treefender, a VR-exclusive 4 player online co-op base-building game <br>where you build your own treefort and defend it against a spacesquid invasion!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build</h2>The treefort of your nostalgic dreams. With intuitive buildtools and many buildpieces to pick from.<br>Find valuable mushrooms spread out across the neigbourhood for Koinz to unlock new, wacky stuff to build.<br>Add decorations to your fort to earn more Koinz.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/c68512d84c04b2c4e2f5f41e14998284.poster.avif?t=1720096938\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/c68512d84c04b2c4e2f5f41e14998284.webm?t=1720096938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/c68512d84c04b2c4e2f5f41e14998284.mp4?t=1720096938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend</h2>Yourself, and your buddies (4 player online co-op) against grumpy space squids, set out to harvest every tree in the universe!<br>Use everything in your Treefender arsenal: slingshots, exploding gardengnomes, makeshift drones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/a0b5f84c32b43195c2c491e3c42f9741.poster.avif?t=1720096938\" width=300 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/a0b5f84c32b43195c2c491e3c42f9741.webm?t=1720096938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Expand</h2>Your treefort with new abilities, wonky buildobjects and wacky weapons you research.<br>The squiddies won't know what hit 'em!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/11aa053d4489b753d4514581ccac4515.poster.avif?t=1720096938\" width=300 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809480/extras/11aa053d4489b753d4514581ccac4515.webm?t=1720096938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
